data.description: Back on Market due to Buyer not being able to qualify. No fault of seller. Fantastic opportunity to live in one of Paloma Creeks most sought after subdivisions, Lakeview! Wont take much to make this 2011 property your own! Priced to sell and only needs paint and carpet. Home is in need of some TLC but has great bones. Granite in all 3 full bathrooms and kitchen. Luxury vinyl plank throughout all major traffic areas. Brand new roof, stone fireplace, SS appliances, and corner lot! You don't want to miss this one!
